{"tid":1330881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】【721香城Online】水魔法師回魔塔","createTime":"2019-07-18T17:33:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T00:04:01.000Z","uid":14220,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5cc87a599af913eaca55e8356c35f376f17af9af","tid":1330881,"uid":14220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:33:59.000Z","msg":"唔知大家仲記唔記得有個畫面係有個玩家拎路邊淋花嘅嗰條水管嚟淋煙頭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(Sorry，搵唔翻嗰條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n我諗我地可以參考一下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">回魔塔</span></span></strong><br />\n回魔塔結構應該大致相同<br />\n(求任務路線鄰近玩家fact check，同埋睇下路線鄰近回魔塔數目，有錯求屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JPFdTTi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJPFdTTi.png&h=dd91dcaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yR3K0yi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyR3K0yi.png&h=68454480&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FnmXA6E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFnmXA6E.png&h=5ce39ea7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">道具</span></span></strong><br />\n<ins>內四角匙</ins><br />\n開啟道具<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M3RsYqv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM3RsYqv.png&h=1bb5a8ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>士巴拿</ins><br />\n解鎖道具<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pu4BRLX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpu4BRLX.png&h=ff182354&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">武器合成</span></span></strong><br />\n<ins>水管</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kRz2NhV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkRz2NhV.png&h=c8eaff9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>水管卡扣(連手擰)</ins><br />\n加固水管與回魔塔嘅連接<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zLyCBbH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzLyCBbH.png&h=d3a79e24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>強化配件</ins></strong><br />\n<ins>水管轉接頭+不同槍頭</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ck92Nj2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCk92Nj2.png&h=8b919d70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ON4ges.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ON4ges.png&h=46552216&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加強水壓<br />\n加上唔同槍頭，可加強單體攻擊力或轉換為範圍技，可攻可守，甚至有槍頭可再加裝寶石作進一步強化<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bzSf7Fn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbzSf7Fn.png&h=d4796822&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">解鎖方法</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/62Yp6xXp7Po\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F62Yp6xXp7Po&d=mJB0HZfowtkqKRKkSYSHE4R92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=c0c05f30\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/62Yp6xXp7Po</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">強化方法</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FW3IbgqWFiY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFW3IbgqWFiY&d=mJB0HZfowtkqKRKkSYSHE4R92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=455141d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FW3IbgqWFiY</a><br />\n\t<br />\n07:45<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">由於角色為初步概念，道具size有待確認</span></span></em></strong>"},{"pid":"fb37ae6a937f1be67f15fa1faf595